    "body": "We should take this as an opportunity to correct our BEM syntax which is currently wrong.\nCurrent is:\n\n```\n{block}--{element}__{modifier}\n```\n\nBut really should be:\n\n```\n{block}__{element}--{modifier}\n```\n",
